2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new deep learning model for feature learning.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new approach for predicting the label of samples using capsule vectors.
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new neural network architecture.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper focuses on improving the performance of image datasets.
